      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KISORA NZ (5) faces the starter for the first time. By Captain Crunch and hails from the Michael Young stable. Showed some ability when a minor placegetter in a recent trial. Capable of taking this out. PAPPINBARRA LADY (3) has been competitive of late and kept the ball rolling last time when 9 metres from the winner in fourth over 2100m at Bunbury. Has the benefit of a good draw. Meets a similar line up and she is a strong winning hope. ESSENCE OF ROYALTY (4) resumes from a spell. Last appeared when a modest tenth over 2185m at Pinjarra 11 months ago. MY SALINA (6) is close to a win after two successive seconds, the latest over 1730m at this track.",
